{"tid":190944,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳 業 坤 買 銀 戒 冧 女","createTime":"2017-04-07T12:50:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T03:36:33.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"645a0ec2cb2f602d9561349bea77522143c3f463","tid":190944,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T12:50:23.000Z","msg":"談及入圍金像獎「最佳新演員」提名，人氣王吳業坤對自己大感驚喜：「起初我以為係指報名名單，真係好驚訝！」在特刊中他穿上西裝及戴上戒指，自揭有浪漫一面：「記得啱啱出嚟兼職做嘢時，曾經努力儲錢買過一隻純銀戒指畀女朋友。至今仍記得送禮嗰陣嘅心情有幾緊張！在我嚟講，戒指特別有意義，唔可以隨便送畀別人，當時我下咗好大決心後先送出去！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170406/photo/bkn-20170406210416897-0406_00862_001_06b.jpg?20170406224854\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170406%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170406210416897-0406_00862_001_06b.jpg%3F20170406224854&h=0ba0d710&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19a18c3ad1749dea39c3a5cec2902a355e763b0e","tid":190944,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T12:55:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea5320fdfdbb20595cbf7ecd59a6637adedb4979","tid":190944,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T12:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ......"},{"pid":"0402dabfac182010244fcb3d7c234f49aee5245a","tid":190944,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T02:31:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"653a02893d66a0156d0b23f1a7741b4defb614e8","tid":190944,"uid":50727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:36:33.000Z","msg":"點解西裝都可以著到咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}